<template>
  <iframeLoading :iframeUrl="iframeUrl"></iframeLoading>
</template>

<script>
import iframeLoading from '@/components/common/iframeLoading'
export default {
  name: "PaymentSequenceSetting",
  created(){
    this.iframeUrl =  '/GoldenStandABS/www/components/PaymentSequence/PaymentSequenceSetting.html?tid='+this.TrustID+'&editable=no'
  },
  data () {
    return {
      iframeUrl: ''
    }
  },
  computed:{
    TrustID() {
      return this.$store.state.productInfo.trustId;
    }
  },
  components: {
    iframeLoading
  }
}
</script>
